
[1]powerfully

   POW'ERFULLY, adv. With great force or energy; potently; mightily; with
   great effect; forcibly; either in a physical or moral sense. Certain
   medicines operate powerfully on the stomach; the practice of virtue is
   powerfully recommended by its utility.
